summary: The Amulet Of The Gods Gives The Player 5 Powers
descriptionHtml:
Amulet Of The Gods

The Amulet Of The Gods Gives The Player 5 Powers:

Voice Of The Gods: No Shout Cooldown.
Lungs Of The Gods: Can Breathe Under Water.
Magicka Of The Gods: 100 Extra Points Of Magicka.
Health Of The Gods: 100 Extra Points Of Health.
Stamina Of The Gods: 100 Extra Points Of Stamina.

The Amulet Can Be Found In A Satchel On The Top Of The Highest Mountain In Skyrim.
That Is All I Can Say, Have Fun Searching.

How To Install: Put The File In The Skyrim Data Folder.
author: JP0005
